16 19–710.1.
17 (a) (1) In this section the following words have the meanings indicated.
18 (2) “Adjunct claims documentation” means an abstract of an enrollee’s
19 medical record which describes and summarizes the diagnosis and treatment of, and
20 services rendered to, the enrollee, including, in the case of trauma rendered in a trauma
